   <p>Head Qts 13<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">th</hi></hi> Ky Cav
<lb/><placeName ref="cwgk:P001014">Columbia</placeName> <date when="1863-12-26">Dec 26<hi rend="sup">th</hi></date>
<lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N00000879">John Boyle</persName><lb/>Agt Genl Ky,</p>
<p>I have arrested Moses Hudleston 2 Lt Co. C. 13<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Ky Cav as a deserter from 1<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">st</hi></hi> Ky Cavalry. and forwarded him to his regiment I recomend <persName ref="cwgk:N00005763">Henry Turner </persName>as, 2<hi rend="sup">d</hi> Lt instead he ^Hudleston^ had never been musterd into service in this Regiment</p>
<p>Very Resply
<lb/>J W Weatherford
<lb/>Col 13 Ky Cav<figure type="hr"/></p>
<p>Henry Turner com 2 Lieut Co<hi rend="sup">y</hi> C. 13 Cav<hi rend="sup">y</hi> 
<lb/><date when="1863-12-26">Dec<hi rend="sup">r</hi> 26. 1863</date><figure type="hr"/>
<lb/>1.2.3.4.5.<pb/></p>
<p>Issue.
<lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N001000">Tho E Bramlette</persName></p>
<p>13 Cav<hi rend="sup">y</hi><figure type="hr"/>
<lb/>Lt. Turner<figure type="hr"/>
<lb/>Coms iss<hi rend="sup">d</hi> &amp; forw<hi rend="sup">d</hi> <date when="1863-12-30">Dec<hi rend="sup">r</hi> 30. 1863</date></p>
